Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.06,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}One time 構成した世界線を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.43,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Loop back なんてあり得ないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:11.43,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}One life 与えられたスクリプトを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:13.81,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}派手に躍らせようか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.06,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}少し迷って　I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:32.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}軽そうに見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:34.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:37.50,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}無価値じゃない　Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}どんな未来だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:45.83,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}思い出すべき過去とか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:52.21,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}存在しないこと知っても構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.43,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:57.03,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}すれ違っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.62,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}絆ほど強さ纏って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:12.85,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}この声を聞いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:16.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:17.63,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}誇れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.38,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Drifting like a flawless ray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}一次成形的世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}已无法再倒带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:11.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}被赋予的人生脚本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:13.81,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}让其大放异彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}感到些许迷茫  I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:32.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}尽管看似玩世不恭
Comment: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:34.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:37.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那并非徒劳  Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}无论未来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:45.83,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那本该唤醒的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:52.21,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}就算是飘渺的存在又何妨
Comment: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
Comment: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:57.03,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}即使擦身而过
Comment: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.32,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}如牵挂般萦绕身旁
Comment: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:12.85,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}能否听到我的呐喊
